- ğŸ” **Quantumâ€‘Safe Cryptography:** Provides protection against quantum attacks through **NIST-standardized** key encapsulation and digital signature algorithms. These are implemented by leading cryptographic experts and built on trusted, **leading libraries in the field**â€”see [liboqs](https://openquantumsafe.org/liboqs/) for contributor details.
- âš™ï¸ **Zero-Hassle Integration:** Integrates easily into Python applications with no dependency on native compilation or low-level build steps.

